<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8"?>
<Subtitle>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>1</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>11893</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>18402</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>鲍比睁开眼睛的时候，一切看上去都没有变化。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>2</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>18403</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>23499</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我的愿望实现了吗？”他问休伊。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>3</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>23500</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>27529</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>休伊打了个哈欠。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>4</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>27530</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>31426</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你得回家自己看看。”他回答。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>5</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>31427</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>40369</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>鲍比转身准备走，正在这时休伊说：“你是不是忘了什么事情？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>6</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>40370</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>45644</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>鲍比抓了抓脑袋，四处看了看。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>7</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>45645</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>51646</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我。”休伊说。他指了指那口井。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>8</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>51647</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>59245</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>鲍比将休伊的壳放回了桶里，把他送回了井底。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>9</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>59246</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>64753</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>然后，鲍比就尽他最快的速度跑回了家，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>10</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>64754</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>69068</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>连声谢谢或再见都没来得及说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>11</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>69069</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>78025</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“有人吗？赛伊？潘瑟？简？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>12</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>78026</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>85523</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>鲍比一边跑进房子里，一边大声叫着其他兄弟姐妹的名字。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>13</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>85524</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>88445</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>没人应声。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>14</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>88446</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>92665</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>鲍比跑进了他和赛伊的房间。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>15</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>92666</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>96433</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>房里只有一张床了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>16</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>96434</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>100924</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>然后，他又跑进了女生的房间里。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>17</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>100925</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>104861</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>那个房间里堆满了旧箱子和书。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>18</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>104862</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>109698</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“耶！”鲍比兴奋地大叫起来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>19</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>109699</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>117024</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他跳起舞来，为自己终于可以独自一人而感到欢喜。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>20</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>117025</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>123108</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>鲍比以前经常想象没有兄弟姐妹会是什么样子。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>21</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>123109</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>130516</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>如果没有兄弟姐妹，他就再也不用分享、等待或排队了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>22</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>130517</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>136872</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“现在没人能对我指手画脚了！”他大声说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>23</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>136873</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>142697</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你到底在干什么？”他身后有人尖声叫道。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>24</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>142698</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>146776</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>鲍比转身看到了他的阿姨。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>25</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>146777</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>150294</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他跑过去给了她一个拥抱。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>26</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>150295</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>156698</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“玛莎阿姨！我看到你太高兴了！”他说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>27</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>156699</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>161917</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你怎么了？你还好吗？”玛莎阿姨问。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>28</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>161918</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>165520</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她用手摸了摸鲍比的额头。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>29</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>165521</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>170938</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我特别好。”鲍比大笑道。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>30</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>170939</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>175045</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“那就好。”玛莎阿姨回答。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>31</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>175046</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>178493</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“因为我们有很多事情要做。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>32</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>178494</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>182442</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她把真空吸尘器递给了鲍比。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>33</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>182443</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>185320</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你可以从楼下的卧室开始。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>34</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>185321</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>188246</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>不要错过任何一个角落！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>35</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>188247</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>192736</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“好的，玛莎阿姨。”鲍比回答。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>36</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>192737</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>195767</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他没刚才那么开心了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>37</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>195768</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>201931</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>鲍比打扫干净卧室后，他突然想起了从前。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>38</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>201932</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>207051</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他和赛伊以前一直假装吸尘器是个怪物。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>39</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>207052</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>214421</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>赛伊会一边追着他四处跑一边叫：“他要吃了你！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>40</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>214422</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>219931</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>鲍比不得不承认，他的哥哥并不总是那么坏的。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>41</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>219932</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>224586</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他们确实曾一起度过很有意思的时光。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>42</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>224587</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>227496</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>玛莎阿姨走了进来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>43</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>227497</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>233824</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你怎么花了这么长时间？”她说着穿上了自己的外套。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>44</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>233825</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>241702</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“嗯，我，嗯......”鲍比支支吾吾地说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>45</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>241703</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>244444</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>玛莎阿姨摇摇头。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>46</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>244445</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>251662</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“没事。”她说，“穿上你的夹克，我们去基弗先生店里。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>47</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>251663</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>256177</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>基弗先生在城里开了一家小杂货店。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>48</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>256178</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>260694</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>潘瑟和简以前很喜欢去那里，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>49</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>260695</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>264724</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>因为基弗先生总是给她们糖果。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>50</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>264725</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>268119</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>无论女孩子们什么时候到家，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>51</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>268120</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>273042</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>简总是会向她的兄弟们展示她得到的糖果。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>52</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>273043</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>277862</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“很好吃！我最喜欢的糖果！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>53</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>277863</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>283175</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她会一边说，一边把一个樱桃味儿的糖扔进嘴里。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>54</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>283176</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>290893</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>但潘瑟总是会把包递给鲍比说：“给你，鲍比，拿点我的糖。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>55</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>290894</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>296245</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>当鲍比和玛莎阿姨朝着杂货店走去的时候，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>56</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>296246</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>301522</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>鲍比加快了速度跟上玛莎阿姨的步子。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>57</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>301523</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>303759</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我要买些蔬菜。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>58</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>303760</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>308791</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>当他们到了基弗先生的店里时，玛莎阿姨说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>59</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>308792</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>315360</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“这是清单。你去拿其他的东西，然后我们在结账台会合。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>60</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>315361</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>319450</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>鲍比无助地看着清单。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>61</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>319451</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>323151</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“但是......”他开口说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>62</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>323152</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>327966</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>然而，玛莎阿姨已经消失在了过道里。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>63</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>327967</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>332736</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“无糖玉米罐头。”鲍比念着清单。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>64</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>332737</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>340799</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他开始在过道里上下寻找，但却始终找不到该往哪里走。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>65</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>340800</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>346528</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“要是潘瑟在就好了。”他低声说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>66</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>346529</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>354000</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“她一定知道这些东西都摆在哪里。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
</Subtitle>